        REVISIONS
        * 3:49 PM 9/5/2025 FUNDEMENTAL FLAW: find-mgGraphCommand DOES NOT HAVE ALL MGGRAPH CMDLET PERMS! And it doesn't throw errors on empty perms, it just returns NOTHING
