Function get-MGOPLastSync {
  <#
    .SYNOPSIS
    get-MGOPLastSync - Get specific Tenant/Org's last AD-MG sync (MGGraph)
    .NOTES
    Author      : Todd Kadrie
    Website     :	https://www.toddomation.com
